        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You can use this package from other Swift packages locally, or share the package through a git hosting provider.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "When you want to release your own package, create a git tag that matches the major, minor, and patch versions of a semantic version and push the tag to your git hosting provider.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "For example, to tag the package with the semantic version ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
